cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR

This paper deals with the problem of estimating 6D poses of objects from images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method uses a deep neural network (cs.LG) and involves iterative refinement of the pose estimation (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of benchmarks for 6D pose estimation (cs.GR).
